  =item B<--mode>
  
  Choose a mode.
  
  =item B<--dyn-mode>
  
  Specify a mode with the path (separated by '::').
  
  =item B<--list-mode>
  
  List available modes.
  
  =item B<--mode-version>
  
  Check minimal version of mode. If not, unknown error.
  
